  "delete|Delete it (not needed)"
  "reference|File as reference"
  "someday|Move to Someday/Maybe"
  "waiting|Move to Waiting For"
  "project|Create/assign to project"
  "area|Assign to area of responsibility"
  "next_action|Create next action"
  "calendar|Schedule on calendar"
)

